title: Darkest Dungeon Build 7668
description:
Build Update #7668 (PC and Mac)


    Performance optimizations on both platforms
    Various stability improvements on both platforms
    Empty cauldrons are now completely indestructible
    Corrected rabies level progression for Rabid Dogs
    Fixed many missing strings
    Fixed inventory error handling when save loading
    Fixed afflicted heroes moving over each other when surprised at the beginning of combat
    Extra row is now auto-added to realm inventory so it will never be full and so you can unequip trinkets
    Fixed tutorial popup showing up in main menu
    Fixed heirloom tooltip rendering issue in raid results
    Added additional quirk incompatibility logic to raid finish
    Fixed Death's Door debuffs applying on restore
